# Nessa CRM Form Design System

Use this design language for all forms. Reference: `components/tasks/inline-task-composer.tsx`.

## Card / container

- **Card**: `border border-neutral-200/60 shadow-md rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden bg-white`
- **Width**: `max-w-[340px] min-w-[320px]` (or `w-full` with those constraints)
- **Header**: `flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3`
- **Title**: `text-[15px] font-semibold text-neutral-900`
- **Content**: `px-5 pb-5 pt-2 space-y-4`

## Field rows (each form row)

- **Row wrapper**: `flex items-center gap-3 pb-3 border-b border-neutral-100`
- **Leading icon**: `h-5 w-5 text-neutral-400 shrink-0` (use `h-4 w-4` for smaller icons e.g. ChevronDown)
- **Optional trailing icon**: same size, same color

## Inputs (no visible border, no focus ring)

- **Title / primary text input**: Use a native `<input type="text">` (not the shadcn Input component) so the caret renders at full height from the first blink. Classes: `flex-1 border-0 bg-transparent p-0 py-1 text-[15px] text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0`
- **Text Input (secondary)**: `h-auto min-h-0 border-0 p-0 bg-transparent shadow-none focus-visible:ring-0 text-[14px] placeholder:text-neutral-400`
- **No focus outline**: add `outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-0 focus-visible:ring-offset-0` on any input/textarea that must have zero focus ring
- **Placeholder**: `placeholder:text-neutral-400`; use `placeholder:italic` for search-style fields
- **Date input**: same base + `text-neutral-700 [color-scheme:light]`

## Select

- **SelectTrigger**: `h-auto min-h-0 border-0 p-0 bg-transparent shadow-none focus:ring-0 focus:ring-offset-0 text-[14px] flex-1 [&>span]:text-neutral-400 data-[placeholder]:text-neutral-400`
- **Chevron (right)**: `h-4 w-4 text-neutral-400 shrink-0`

## Textarea

- **Textarea**: `flex-1 min-h-0 border-0 rounded-none p-0 bg-transparent shadow-none outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-0 focus-visible:ring-offset-0 text-[14px] resize-none placeholder:text-neutral-400`

## Tags / chips (e.g. assignees, multi-select)

- **Chip**: `inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-neutral-100/80 border border-neutral-200/60 pl-1 pr-2 py-0.5 text-[13px] text-neutral-700`
- **Avatar in chip**: `h-5 w-5 shrink-0`; fallback `text-[9px] bg-neutral-400 text-white`
- **Remove (X)**: `hover:bg-neutral-200 rounded-full p-0.5 text-neutral-400 hover:text-neutral-700`, icon `h-3.5 w-3.5`

## Dropdown / popover list

- **Container**: `rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/80 bg-white shadow-lg max-h-[200px] overflow-y-auto py-1.5`
- **Item**: `w-full flex items-center gap-2.5 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-neutral-50 text-left text-[13px] text-neutral-800`
- **Empty state**: `text-[12px] text-neutral-500 italic py-2`

## Validation / errors

- **Error text**: `text-[11px] text-red-500` with `ml-8` or `pl-8` and `-mt-1` or `-mt-2` so it aligns under the field content (not under the icon)

## Optional / “Add more” link

- **Toggle button**: `flex items-center gap-3 w-full text-left text-[13px] text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-700 py-2`

## Primary submit button

- **Button**: `w-full h-11 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-800 text-white text-[14px] font-semibold rounded-[14px] mt-1`

## Close / icon buttons (header)

- **Ghost icon button**: `h-8 w-8 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-500`, icon `h-[18px] w-[18px]`

## Helper / hints (keyboard shortcuts)

- **Row**: `flex items-center justify-between pt-2 text-[11px] text-neutral-400`
- **Keycap**: `inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-100/80 text-neutral-500 font-mono text-[10px]`

## Typography summary

| Use            | Class |
|----------------|--------|
| Section title  | `text-[15px] font-semibold text-neutral-900` |
| Field value    | `text-[15px]` (title), `text-[14px]` (others) |
| Placeholder    | `placeholder:text-neutral-400` |
| Chips / tags   | `text-[13px] text-neutral-700` |
| Dropdown item  | `text-[13px] text-neutral-800` |
| Optional link  | `text-[13px] text-neutral-500` |
| Error          | `text-[11px] text-red-500` |
| Helper / kbd   | `text-[11px] text-neutral-400`, keycap `text-[10px]` |

## Alignment

- One icon left, control in middle (`flex-1 min-w-0`), optional icon right.
- Errors and dropdowns: offset by icon column (e.g. `ml-8` or `pl-8`).
- Keep `gap-3` between icon and content; `space-y-4` between major sections; `pb-3 border-b border-neutral-100` between rows.
